WEBVTT

00:00.349 --> 00:02.083
Everybody knows about the Wright brothers.

00:02.445 --> 00:04.192
They were the first in fly.

00:04.980 --> 00:07.573
These guys had sneakers that blew people's minds.

00:08.481 --> 00:09.773
Women loved their sneakers,...

00:10.159 --> 00:11.835
...men wanted to be in their sneakers.

00:12.185 --> 00:14.455
While everybody else was stuck on crisscross laces,...

00:14.684 --> 00:16.540
...the Wright brothers were the first to do bars.

00:17.212 --> 00:18.808
But their flyest idea of all,...

00:19.381 --> 00:21.829
...wearing sneakers to formal events.

00:23.259 --> 00:24.548
They also invented airplanes.

00:25.237 --> 00:26.403
That's my report on the Wright Brothers.

00:27.153 --> 00:27.977
The first in fly.

00:28.819 --> 00:29.859
Excellent research.

